<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Badge Poser</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Flat and Clean.">
    <meta name="author" content="Jenil Gogari">

    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->

    {% stylesheets
        '@PUGXBadgeBundle/Resources/public/css/bootstrap.css'
        '@PUGXBadgeBundle/Resources/public/css/bootstrap-responsive.css'
        '@PUGXBadgeBundle/Resources/public/css/custom.css'

        filter='?yui_css' %}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset_url }}" />
    {% endstylesheets %}
</head>

<body class="preview" id="top" data-spy="scroll" data-target=".subnav" data-offset="80">

<div id="container" class="container-narrow">

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>Badge Poser</h1>
        <p class="lead">Pimp your README!</p>
        <p class="lead">
            <a href="https://packagist.org/packages/pugx/badge-poser"><img style="max-width:100%;" alt="Latest Stable Version" src="{{ path('pugx_badge_version',{'repository': 'pugx/badge-poser'}) }}"></a>
            <a target="_blank" href="http://travis-ci.org/PUGX/badge-poser"><img src="https://secure.travis-ci.org/PUGX/badge-poser.png" /></a>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid bundles">
        <div class="span12">
            <article>
                <h3 class="centered-content"><strong>Be a poser!</strong></h3>
                <p>
                    Use shields for your <a href="https://packagist.org">packagist.org</a> repository, showing how many times your project has been downloaded from Packagist.org or its latest stable version.
                </p>
                <hr class="styled">
                <h3 class="centered-content">Show the markdown for your Badges</h3>
                <form id="generate-form" action="{{ path('pugx_snippet_all') }}" class="form-inline centered-content">
                  <input type="text" name="repository" class="input" placeholder="vendor/repository">
                  <button id="generate" class="btn">Show</button>
                </form>
                <p class="centered-content"><small >Put the following snippets in your README.markdown:</small></p>

                <div id="badges">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Latest Stable Version <img class="pull-right spinned" id="latest_stable_version_img" src="{{ path('pugx_badge_version',{'repository': repository}) }}"></h4>
                        <pre id="latest_stable_version_markdown" class="prettyprint">[![Latest Stable Version]({{ url('pugx_badge_version',{'repository': repository}) }})]({{ url('pugx_badge_packagist',{'repository': repository}) }})</pre>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Total downloads <img class="pull-right spinned" id="total_img" src="{{ path('pugx_badge',{'repository': repository}) }}"></h4>
                        <pre id="total_markdown" class="prettyprint">[![Total Downloads]({{ url('pugx_badge',{'repository': repository}) }})]({{ url('pugx_badge_packagist',{'repository': repository}) }})</pre>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Monthly downloads <img class="pull-right spinned" id="monthly_img" src="{{ path('pugx_badge_stat',{'repository': repository, 'type':'monthly'}) }}"></h4>
                        <pre id="monthly_markdown" class="prettyprint">[![Monthly Downloads]({{ url('pugx_badge_stat',{'repository': repository, 'type':'monthly'}) }})]({{ url('pugx_badge_packagist',{'repository': repository}) }})</pre>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Daily downloads <img class="pull-right spinned" id="daily_img" src="{{ path('pugx_badge_stat',{'repository': repository, 'type':'daily'}) }}"></h4>
                        <pre id="daily_markdown" class="prettyprint">[![Daily Downloads]({{ url('pugx_badge_stat',{'repository': repository, 'type':'daily'}) }})]({{ url('pugx_badge_packagist',{'repository': repository}) }})</pre>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Latest Unstable Version <img class="pull-right spinned" id="latest_unstable_version_img" src="{{ path('pugx_badge_version_latest',{'repository': repository, 'latest':'unstable'}) }}"></h4>
                        <pre id="latest_unstable_version_markdown" class="prettyprint">[![Latest Unstable Version]({{ url('pugx_badge_version_latest',{'repository': repository, 'latest':'unstable'}) }})]({{ path('pugx_badge_packagist',{'repository': repository}) }})</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<div class=" container-narrow">

    <hr>

    <p class="footer">Badge Poser is a <a href="http://pugx.github.io" target="_blank">PUGX</a> initiative.</p>

    <hr>

    <div class="row-fluid">
        <h4>Sponsors</h4>
        <ul class="thumbnails">
            <li class="span4">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <span class="badge pull-right">Server</span>
                    <a href="http://www.ideato.it"  title="Ideato | Web ideas for sale"><img src="{{ asset('bundles/pugxbadge/img/ideato-srl.png') }}" alt="Ideato SRL" style="width: 300px; height: 75px"></a>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="span4">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <span class="badge pull-right">Monitoring and Statistics</span>
                    <a href="http://tvision.github.io" title="Tvision software team"><img src="{{ asset('bundles/pugxbadge/img/tvision.jpg') }}" alt="Tvision-team" style="  height: 75px;"></a>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="span4">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                    <span class="badge pull-right">SSL certificate</span>
                    <a href="godaddy.com" title="Godaddy Free opensource SSL certificates"><img src="{{ asset('bundles/pugxbadge/img/godaddy-logo.png') }}" alt="Go-Daddy" style="  width: 200px; height: 75px"></a>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>


<a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/PUGX/badge-poser"><img style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_darkblue_121621.png" alt="Fork me on GitHub"></a>

